        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: GluR2 measured with western blot in presynaptic synaptosome fractions.\n\n8/9/2017 Pim\n- Experiments involve quantification of plasma membrane/surface levels of receptors via biotinylation assay.\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Slices 400 lm thick were prepared from cortex and hippocampi of adult Wistar rats" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" ;
